  "abstract": "There are no readymade formulas that one can apply over large areas to obtain a quantum yield jump over large areas from the current National average of 800 kg ha pods of groundnut pods to the yields of the order reported from ICRISAT (4-5 t ha in kharif and 6-8 t ha in Rabi).....",
